- ŌØī Never paste resolved values (ŌĆ£4pxŌĆØ) where a token exists.
- ŌØī Never use `!important` to fight design-system styles; fix specificity instead.
- ŌØī Do not restructure JSX/markup unless required for `.gamma-icon` or `data-gamma-*` attributes; this is a CSS migration.
- ŌØī Do not change visual layout/positioning logic (flex/grid structure) unless itŌĆÖs broken by tokenization.

